danak Obs., Uzbekistan, Buryakan Obs., Armenia, Konkoly Obs., Hungary, and La Palma Obs., Spain. Photometric data are only available in electronic form at the CDS via anonymous ftp to cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr (130.79.128.5) or via http://cdsweb.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/qcat?J/A+A/463/1017},
